== bed enter / exit ==

== player / console command ==
<cmdarg:1> to infinite
<cmdarg1> to infinite

== entity death ==

<drops:0> to infinite (mat name to lower case)
<droppedexp>

== inventory click ==

<clickeditemenchant:index>
<inventorysize>

